    currentPartsRef.current = [];
    assistantCreatedRef.current = false;
    // Keep messages on screen — tagged-dedup handles ID reconciliation
    onSessionIdChangeRef.current?.(doneData.sessionId);
  }
```

Note: The `doneData` type is also updated to include `messageIds` in preparation for Phase 3. This is harmless — the field is optional and ignored if absent.

