### 2. `apps/server/src/routes/sessions.ts` — POST /:id/messages

Modify the done event handling (around lines 194-207). Currently it sends a second `done` event only when the session ID was remapped. Change it to always include `messageIds` when available:

**Before:**
```typescript
if (event.type === 'done') {
  const actualInternalId = runtime.getInternalSessionId(sessionId);
  if (actualInternalId && actualInternalId !== sessionId) {
    logger.debug('[POST /messages] session ID remapped', {
      sessionId,
      internalId: actualInternalId,
    });
    // Send a redirect hint so the client can update its session ID
